title: How to re start after a set up error
content: 75yr old newby trying to set up first phone. I missed the "skip transfer data" prompt and am now stuck in a "transferring data" loop that I cannot find my way back from. Obviously it cannot trf. data from a non existent phone. Any suggestions would be gratefully received.;
